thread.title: Failure of Congress to pass a budget would create instability -White House
thread.title_full: Failure of Congress to pass a budget would create instability -White House | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: Failure of Congress to pass a budget would create instability -White House
text:
WASHINGTON, Sept 8 The White House said on Tuesday the U.S. Congress would contribute to instability if it does not pass a budget.
White House spokesman Josh Earnest said the Obama administration is confident a bipartisan agreement can be reached.
(Reporting by Julia Edwards ; Editing by Mohammad Zargham )
